Using the .format() Method - Exercise #3
Create three variables - companies, quarter, and sales_performance_prediction that store the following information, respectively:

companies - 'Company A' and 'Company B'

quarter - 1, 2, 3, 4

sales_performance_prediction - 'increase', 'decrease', 'remain the same'.



companies=['Company A','Company B']
quarter=[1,2,3,4]
sales_performance_prediction=['increase','decrease','remain the same']
